<h2>Privacy</h2>

<p>ONETUG is committed to protecting your privacy and developing technology that gives you the most powerful and safe online experience. This Statement of Privacy applies to the ONETUG website and smartphone applications and governs data collection and usage. By using the ONETUG website and smartphone applications, you consent to the data practices described in this statement.</p>
<p><strong>Collection of your Personal Information</strong></p>
<p>
