<p><strong>Use of your Personal Information</strong></p>
<p>ONETUG may collect and uses your personal information to operate the ONETUG website and smartphone applications and deliver the services you have requested. ONETUG also uses your personally identifiable information to inform you of other products or services available from ONETUG and its affiliates. ONETUG may also contact you via surveys to conduct research about your opinion of current services or of potential new services that may be offered.
